data.title: Olivia Brooks & Jamie Spencer's Baby Registry
data.meta_description: Visit the baby registry of Olivia Brooks and Jamie Spencer of Brighouse, England, at MyRegistry.com and celebrate on their expected due date, Sunday, September 29, 2024.
data.text:
You’ll notice that Olivia & Jamie have added items from Amazon.co.uk and Mamas & Papas. That’s the beauty of having a registry at MyRegistry.com—our members can add items from literally any store!

Spot something nice? Click BUY THIS GIFT, and don’t worry if you’re redirected to another site. Just put the item in your cart and check out!

Need help? Reach us 7 days a week via Live Chat or by calling 201.886.1000
